name: Traditional House #5 - Honai
description: It's a pixel sprite 120x120 upscale to 1200x1200 of traditional house from Papua, Indonesia. Honai commonly used for Papuan that live in the mountains. It's a round-shaped house with a roof made from wood, straw, dry grass or even reeds. If you notice, this house didn't have windows, but in the middle, Papuan create a place for a bonfire. Honai consists of two floors.
